<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_script"><sys_ui_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description/><global>false</global><ignore_in_now_experience>false</ignore_in_now_experience><name>x_376096_cxp.config</name><script><![CDATA[var x_376096_cxp = x_376096_cxp || {};

x_376096_cxp.config = (function () {
	"use strict";

	/* eslint no-undef: "error" */
	if (x_376096_cxp.config && x_376096_cxp.config.type == 'config') {
		return x_376096_cxp.config;
	}

	var callbacks = [];
	var initialLoaded = false;
	var module = {
		on_ready: function (cb) {
			if (initialLoaded) {
				cb(module);
			} else {
				callbacks.push(cb);
			}
		},
		type: "config"
	};

	var ready = x_376096_cxp.config ? x_376096_cxp.config.ready : null;
	x_376096_cxp.get_window(function ($window) {
		var newRecord = $window.document.getElementById('sys_row');
		module.update = function (cb) {
			var ga = new $window.GlideAjax('ConfigHelper').setScope('x_376096_cxp');
			ga.addParam('sysparm_name', 'generate');
			ga.addParam('table', $window.NOW.targetTable);
			ga.addParam('sys_id', $window.NOW.sysId);
			ga.addParam('new_record', newRecord && newRecord.value === '-1');
			ga.getXMLAnswer(function (config) {
				if (config) {
					config = JSON.parse(config);
					for (var attr in config) {
						module[attr] = config[attr];
					}

					cb(module);
				}
			});
		};

		var ga = new $window.GlideAjax('ConfigHelper').setScope('x_376096_cxp');
		ga.addParam('sysparm_name', 'generate');
		ga.addParam('table', $window.NOW.targetTable);
		ga.addParam('sys_id', $window.NOW.sysId);
		ga.addParam('new_record', newRecord && newRecord.value === '-1');
		ga.getXMLAnswer(function (config) {
			init(JSON.parse(config));
		});

		//var initialConfig = JSON.parse(ga.getXMLWait().documentElement.getAttribute('answer'));
		//init(initialConfig);
	});

	return module;

	function init(initialConfig) {
		for (var attr in initialConfig) {
			module[attr] = initialConfig[attr];
		}

		initialLoaded = true;
		if (ready) {
			ready(module);
		}

		callbacks.forEach(function (cb) {
			cb(module);
		});
	}
})();
